        "Home > Gamemastering > Bestiary > Vermin > Crab Family > Crab Table of Contents Crabs are small crustaceans with eight legs and two pincers or claws. Aquatic scavengers, crabs can also survive on land for some time, but must return to the water or suffocate. Crab (CR 1/4)",
